cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper deals with image synthesis using deep convolutional networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves user interaction and control over the generated images, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR). The use of adversarial networks and conditioning on sketches and color strokes suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves generating realistic images, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
